   'Keyed by partyId (screening lifecycle per party stays ordered); payloads carry IDs, statuses, list-version and score — party details by reference, not value. ScreeningRequested (owner: orchestration) feeds vendor adapters and audit; ScreeningCompleted feeds onboarding and audit; ScreeningHitCreated (with hitId as the idempotency anchor) feeds case management. All schema-governed, all in the event catalogue.',
